{
  "texts": [
    "In conclusion, the named entity recognition investigation has been conducted for a number of Indian languages.",
    "A comparably large amount of work has been done in this field for several languages, including Marathi, Hindi, English and Punjabi.",
    "On the other hand, there hasn't been as much research done on named entity recognition for languages like Telugu and Sindhi etc.",
    "When compared to languages that had basic language processing capabilities, languages that already had enough accuracy in their processing tools needed a lot less time and money development.",
    "In this article, we explored comprehensive range of machine learning approaches for NER in Indian languages."
  ]
}